  "texts": [
    "The remaining datasets do not have clear documentation about their collection practices.",
    "Where applicable, we further filter the datasets to contain the more opinionated tweets; we take the \"pro\" and \"anti\" subsets of the Twitter Climate Change Sentiment Dataset and the Brexit Polarity Tweets Dataset, excluding the \"neutral\" sentiment cases.",
    "Lastly, all datasets are filtered to contain only tweets written before March 2022 in English.",
    "Here we list the exact prompts used to generate tweets, and provide further details on the generation model fine-tuning.",
    "Examples of output from each of the LLMs in response to each prompting strategy can be seen in Table 8."
